", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75207235_409530041508063_1594896824332022275_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=u-YEIIqr2M8Q7kNvgGFmLhy&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBvTodRB6Nl9JE7mRhaPsW8aBomjY_umixmzvoScBkDkA&oe=6708FBCF"}, "display_name": "Blade & Gun", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Storyline\n\nIn the sprawling metropolis of Neo-Tokyo, the city is shrouded in darkness and neon lights. Crime lords and rogue AI have taken control, turning the once-thriving city into a dystopian nightmare. Amidst the chaos, you are a ninja warrior with a unique edge\u2014armed with both a traditional katana and a high-tech gun. As the last guardian of the ancient ninja order, your mission is clear: defend the city from relentless assaults and restore order.\nKey Features\n\n1. Immersive VR Experience\n\n    Enter a fully immersive virtual reality world where you feel every swing of your katana and every shot from your gun. The high-fidelity graphics and realistic soundscapes make you feel like you\u2019re truly in Neo-Tokyo.\n", "short_description": "Storyline\n\nIn the sprawling metropolis of Neo-Tokyo, the city is shrouded in darkness and neon lights. Crime lords and rogue AI have taken control, turning the once-thriving city into a dystopian nightmare. Amidst the chaos, you are a ninja warrior with a unique edge\u2014armed with both a traditional katana and a high-tech gun. As the last guardian of the ancient ninja order, your mission is clear: defend the city from relentless assaults and restore order."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/blade-gun/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "KERR Invention", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/blade-gun", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES